s="dcr-notra3"><div aria-hidden="true" class="dcr-13832xi"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 11 11"><path d="M5.4 0C2.4 0 0 2.4 0 5.4s2.4 5.4 5.4 5.4 5.4-2.4 5.4-5.4S8.4 0 5.4 0zm3 6.8H4.7V1.7h.7L6 5.4l2.4.6v.8z"></path></svg> This article is more than <strong>22 years old</strong></div></div><h1 class="dcr-d5iddn">Douglas Adams dies at age 49</h1><div class="dcr-1nvgr5i">This article is more than 22 years old</div></div></div></div><div data-gu-name="standfirst" class="dcr-1yi1cnj"><div class=" dcr-cn68uf">Creator of The Hitch Hiker's Guide to the Galaxy bequeaths memorable insights on life, the universe and everything<br /><br /><br /> <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,490971,00.html" data-link-name="in standfirst link">Obituary</a> <br /> <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,489981,00.html" data-link-name="in standfirst link">Actor Stephen Fry pays tribute to a friend</a> <br /> <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,490372,00.html" data-link-name="in standfirst link">A Lament for Douglas Adams by Richard Dawkins</a> <br /> <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,6109,491791,00.html" data-link-name="in standfirst link">Planetary tribute to Hitch Hiker author as Arthurdent named</a></div></div><div data-gu-name="lines" class="dcr-kt8blz"><div class="dcr-14emo0l"><div class="dcr-ich95x"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="13" viewBox="0 0 1300 13" preserveAspectRatio="none" stroke="var(--article-border)" stroke-width="1" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="dcr-194w08h"><line x1="0" x2="1300" y1="0.5" y2="0.5"></line><line x1="0" x2="1300" y1="4.5" y2="4.5"></line><line x1="0" x2="1300" y1="8.5" y2="8.5"></line><line x1="0" x2="1300" y1="12.5" y2="12.5"></line></svg></div></div></div><aside data-gu-name="meta" class="dcr-1rbr3jc"><div class="dcr-14emo0l"><div class=" dcr-1v9sla6"><div class="dcr-5oiine"><div class="dcr-1kpcv08"><div><address aria-labe